tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE audit_trail (
    audit_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id UUID,
    action VARCHAR(50),
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    details JSONB
);

CREATE TABLE transaction_log ( 
    log_id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
    user_id INT, 
    transaction_date TIMESTAMP, 
    action VARCHAR(50), 
    details TEXT 
);
